title: Fra Lippo Lippi - In A Brilliant White (CD, 2002)
description:
Last album released by Norway's finest, Fra Lippo Lippi, though in fact this is a solo album by vocalist Per Sorensen.

Released exclusively in the Phillipines in 2002.

1.   Story Of A Broken Heart
2.   Faithful
3.   Will I Recognize
4.   Come On
5.   Later
6.   Wish We Were Two
7.   Ordinary Guy
8.   Stay
9.   Who Is Your Buddha
10.  If I Knew Then

I've also included some scans of the CD cover, etc.
